{"tid":2388424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(毒撚j) 情侶飛鵝山被「照田雞」惹爭執","createTime":"2021-01-31T06:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T14:56:49.000Z","uid":156652,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b38fb6ee9cb1d109619216c008640f208afaab50","tid":2388424,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:23:27.000Z","msg":"今（31日）凌晨零時許，警方接獲2男女報案指，在黃大仙飛鵝山道近山頂，被12名大漢掌摑。警員接報到場，在附近截查多人，初步調查後獲放行，男女事主則沒有受傷，無需送院。警方暫列作糾紛處理。<br />\n警方指，一名28歲男子及一名24歲女子，兩人情侶關係，當時在車內聊天，突然有9男3女用手機電筒照向車內，情侶不滿被冒犯，遂下車與眾人理論。惟對方人多勢眾，於是報警處理。經調查後，男女沒有被掌摑，但該9男3女涉嫌違限聚令，每人被票控5000元。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb507bb9a90086701943ed54313a2401321f096","tid":2388424,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:23:45.000Z","msg":"wow"},{"pid":"6bad52b357a53e67baf6cd401be52ffb44c3d759","tid":2388424,"uid":69157,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:31:43.000Z","msg":"抵死 以為自己好有趣係度照照照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1b13accda526ffb2c6f06d12fd56877be9b9c0","tid":2388424,"uid":384324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:32:30.000Z","msg":"條女有sp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d76b4c05792d57eac51da860c8754bdd7d0fa6a","tid":2388424,"uid":88263,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:54:58.000Z","msg":"9男3女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰3條女好忙下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a1fb1b1048d644d216c3fa6061302e39ee5a93","tid":2388424,"uid":249960,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:06:58.000Z","msg":"咁就6萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行行下山就位位5千，成班智障仔"},{"pid":"1b92d47757ba88132b9bf41b30492ba5dff37e5e","tid":2388